715674f-a.title: Manhattan: 153rd Street (West) - Amsterdam Avenue
715674f-a.text:
526-500 West 153rd Street, west of, adjoining, and at the
S.W. corner of Amsterdam Avonue. St. Catherine's Roman Catholic
Church and Rectory adjoins the corner; the Washington Eeights Meth-
odist Episcopal Church is at the corner. The rest of the buildings
on this block are all three-story frame houses.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 377.
